# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🚀 FRONTEND TO PRODUCTION — LEARNING CHECKLIST
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# Instructions:
#   [ ] = Not started
#   [~] = In progress
#   [x] = Completed
#
# Track your progress as you go through each module.
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 📚 CONCEPTS (Theory & Foundations)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Read Docker concepts and understand containerization
[ ] Read CI/CD concepts and understand pipelines
[ ] Read VPS & Domain concepts
[ ] Read Environment Management concepts
[ ] Read Nginx concepts
[ ] Read SSL & Security concepts


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 01: LOCAL DEVELOPMENT SETUP
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Understand project scaffolding with Vite
[ ] Configure ESLint and Prettier
[ ] Set up folder structure for production-grade app
[ ] Understand the difference between dev and production builds
[ ] Run the sample React app locally
[ ] Understand HMR (Hot Module Replacement)


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 02: ENVIRONMENT MANAGEMENT
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Understand .env file usage in React/Vite
[ ] Learn `.env.development`, `.env.production`, `.env.staging`
[ ] Understand VITE_ prefix for exposing env variables
[ ] Learn about secrets management (never commit secrets)
[ ] Understand runtime vs build-time environment variables
[ ] Set up environment-specific configurations


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 03: DOCKER FUNDAMENTALS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Install Docker Desktop
[ ] Understand Docker images vs containers
[ ] Learn Dockerfile syntax (FROM, COPY, RUN, CMD, EXPOSE)
[ ] Build your first Docker image for a React app
[ ] Run a container from your image
[ ] Understand .dockerignore
[ ] Learn docker commands (build, run, ps, stop, rm, logs)


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 04: DOCKER IMAGE BUILD & OPTIMIZATION
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Understand single-stage vs multi-stage builds
[ ] Write a multi-stage Dockerfile for React
[ ] Optimize Docker layer caching
[ ] Reduce image size (from ~1GB to ~25MB)
[ ] Learn about Alpine vs Debian base images
[ ] Tag and version Docker images properly
[ ] Push image to Docker Hub


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 05: DOCKER COMPOSE & NETWORKING
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Understand docker-compose.yml syntax
[ ] Set up multi-service application (frontend + backend + db)
[ ] Learn Docker networking (bridge, host, custom networks)
[ ] Use volumes for persistent data
[ ] Manage environment variables in Compose
[ ] Learn docker-compose commands (up, down, logs, build)


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 06: VPS SETUP & DEPLOYMENT
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Choose a VPS provider (DigitalOcean / AWS / Hetzner)
[ ] Create and configure a VPS instance
[ ] SSH into your server
[ ] Set up a non-root user with sudo access
[ ] Configure firewall (UFW)
[ ] Install Docker on the VPS
[ ] Deploy your Docker container to the VPS
[ ] Understand the difference between VPS, shared hosting, and PaaS


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 07: DOMAIN MAPPING & DNS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Purchase or configure a domain name
[ ] Understand DNS records (A, AAAA, CNAME, MX, TXT)
[ ] Point domain to your VPS IP address
[ ] Set up subdomains (e.g., api.yourapp.com)
[ ] Understand DNS propagation
[ ] Learn about DNS providers (Cloudflare, Route53, Namecheap)


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 08: NGINX REVERSE PROXY & SSL
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Install and configure Nginx
[ ] Set up Nginx as a reverse proxy
[ ] Configure Nginx for React SPA (handle client-side routing)
[ ] Install SSL certificate with Let's Encrypt + Certbot
[ ] Set up auto-renewal for SSL certificates
[ ] Understand HTTP to HTTPS redirect
[ ] Optimize Nginx for performance (gzip, caching headers)


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 09: CI/CD PIPELINE WITH GITHUB ACTIONS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Understand GitHub Actions concepts (workflows, jobs, steps)
[ ] Create a basic workflow file (.yml)
[ ] Set up build and test automation
[ ] Add linting to the pipeline
[ ] Build Docker image in GitHub Actions
[ ] Push Docker image to registry from CI
[ ] Set up GitHub Secrets for sensitive data
[ ] Trigger deployments on push to main


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 10: AUTOMATED DEPLOYMENT
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Set up SSH-based deployment from GitHub Actions
[ ] Implement zero-downtime deployment strategy
[ ] Learn blue-green deployment
[ ] Learn rolling deployment
[ ] Set up rollback mechanism
[ ] Automate database migrations (if applicable)
[ ] Set up deployment notifications (Slack/Discord)


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 11: MONITORING & LOGGING
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Set up application health checks
[ ] Configure uptime monitoring (UptimeRobot / Betterstack)
[ ] Set up error tracking (Sentry)
[ ] Implement structured logging
[ ] Set up server monitoring (htop, df, free)
[ ] Learn about log aggregation
[ ] Set up alerting for critical issues


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 12: ENTERPRISE BEST PRACTICES
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Security hardening checklist
[ ] Performance optimization checklist
[ ] Implement CSP (Content Security Policy) headers
[ ] Set up rate limiting
[ ] Learn about CDN usage (Cloudflare, AWS CloudFront)
[ ] Understand horizontal scaling
[ ] Learn about container orchestration (K8s basics)
[ ] Code review and PR workflow


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🏗️ PRACTICE PROJECTS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[ ] Project 01: Deploy a Personal Portfolio
[ ] Project 02: Deploy an E-commerce Dashboard
[ ] Project 03: Deploy a SaaS Application


# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🎉 CONGRATULATIONS! You've completed the Frontend to Production guide!
